    OBJECTS a=innerArrival FIXED PANEL
    PROPERTIES (a) nameDepartmentStoreInnerArrival, waybillInnerArrival SHOWIF departmentStoreInnerArrival(a), seriesWaybillInnerArrival SHOWIF departmentStoreInnerArrival(a),
